QuestData.Title: Explorers' League Document (1 of 6)
QuestData.Description: The document bears the Explorers' League crest and contains extensive information on the indigenous creatures of Loch Modan. Sooty smudges lead you to believe it was likely stolen by the Dark Iron spies in the area.$B$BYou recall mention of missing documents at the Explorers' League building in Thelsamar.
QuestData.LogDescription: Return the Explorers' League Document to Torren Squarejaw in Thelsamar.
QuestData.RewardText: Hello, $G sonny:lass;! You seem to have found one of our stolen documents, eh?$B$BThank you kindly for bringing it back to us. We'll gladly lend some coin as thanks for its return.
